abstract_ts:
We discuss the asymptotic expansions of certain products of Bernoulli numbers and factorials, e.g., \[ \prod_{
u=1}^n |B_{2
u}| \quad 	ext{and} \quad \prod_{
u=1}^n (k 
u)!^{
u^r} \quad 	ext{as} \quad n 	o \infty \] for integers $k \geq 1$ and $r \geq 0$. Our main interest is to determine exact expressions, in terms of known constants, for the asymptotic constants of these expansions and to show some relations among them.
